CROWLORD

CROWLORD crawls from under the fallen base. He looks around crawling 
on the ground quietly. He drops to charges and sets them to 10 
seconds. He pulls himself to his feet and starts to run he trips and 
falls down right by the charges. His eyes closes.

His eyes open. He looks over to the charges. "shit" The charge says 
3...2...1. Just then a large boom is heard as the 2 charges explode.
